quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Composition[/h1]

Next, we can create the [b]Person [/b]class, which includes the [b]Birthday [/b]class.[code format="cpp"]#include <string>
[b]#include "Birthday.h"[/b]

class Person {
 public:
  Person(string n, Birthday b)
  : name(n),
   bd(b)
  {
  }
 private:
  string name;
  [b]Birthday [/b]bd;
};[/code]
The Person class has a [b]name [/b]and a [b]Birthday [/b]member, and a constructor to initialize them.
Ensure that the corresponding header files are included.
[note]More on [b]Composition [/b]coming up in the next lesson![/note]
